All requests which exceed the cumulative limit of $2,000.00 shall be reviewed
by the Town Administrator and then the Board of Selectmen who shall forward
such requests to the Board of Finance who shall have the power to approve or
deny such requests, up to a cumulative total of ten (10) percent of the agency's
total budget for the Fiscal Year